Returns and exchanges are only available within 7 days of product receipt.
The seller will pay the delivery fee in the event of seller negligence such as product defects or misdelivery.
The buyer will pay the delivery fee in the event of a simple change of heart or mistaken order.
The exchange delivery fee is $5 (round-trip delivery fee), and the return fee is $2.5 (one-way).
Products that have lost value due to opening or damage cannot be refunded or exchanged.

- Please contact us within 7 days of receipt for returns or exchanges due to product defects.
- Refunds or exchanges due to a change of heart are not available.
- Items returned without notice may not be processed.
- Refunds or exchanges are unavailable for products damaged during storage.
- The return delivery fee for exchanges or refunds is OOO.
